{"tid":525434,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"又一間ig 黑店 葉氏雙肥","createTime":"2018-01-10T15:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T05:58:49.000Z","uid":89901,"like":10,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f7358b7a14ad8dcd288040df1548978e0b2069","tid":525434,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"無錯 係ig shop買野係我戇鳩<br />\n以為佢有youtube channel 有出自己樣 <br />\n就會比較可信<br />\n<br />\n事實上係唔會嘅<br />\n天下ig shop一樣黑<br />\n我買嘅野係好少錢 所以拎唔拎得返都冇所謂<br />\n咁用小小錢就可以警剔有想係呢間野買野嘅人<br />\n覺得好值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就12月7號左右入數 <br />\n佢話7至10日會有貨<br />\n有貨再通知 <br />\n我十二月尾都仲未收到<br />\n之後再問就推到話一月頭<br />\n咁我唔得閒 除咗等我都冇其他野可以做<br />\n咁依家一月頭都過咗啦 問佢就無視我 <br />\n而佢ig shop 就持續update <br />\n如果有人要係到買野就請三思啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/234242_873d0278611bd163b3d98e05eeafa657.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F234242_873d0278611bd163b3d98e05eeafa657.png&h=181404bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/234244_bbe6f08179e153815347dd1a5dce1c38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F234244_bbe6f08179e153815347dd1a5dce1c38.png&h=b902bc1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/234246_4802d076a48aac775bc3f68cb49e4064.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F234246_4802d076a48aac775bc3f68cb49e4064.png&h=e2c8158a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/234248_a21811f0696f8b3989e5ea3fbcda0d10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F234248_a21811f0696f8b3989e5ea3fbcda0d10.png&h=9c22c988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/